blocks.en:
flowchart LR
  A[Frame arrives] --> B{seq present?}
  B -- no --> P[Pass up: count tagless]
  B -- yes --> C{first after reset?}
  C -- yes --> P2[Accept, set RecovSeqNum]
  C -- no --> D{seen in history window?}
  D -- yes --> X[Discard duplicate]
  D -- no --> P3[Accept, update window]

blocks.zh:
flowchart LR
  A[帧到达] --> B{有序列号?}
  B -- 无 --> P[向上传递: 计无标签包]
  B -- 有 --> C{复位后首包?}
  C -- 是 --> P2[接受, 设 RecovSeqNum]
  C -- 否 --> D{在历史窗口内见过?}
  D -- 是 --> X[丢弃重复包]
  D -- 否 --> P3[接受, 更新窗口]
